<div class="modal fade" id="qualityInspectionsHelp" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="qualityInspectionsHelpLabel" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="modal-dialog modal-lg modal-dialog-scrollable">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="modal-header">
                <h5 class="modal-title" id="qualityInspectionsHelpLabel">Quality Inspections Help</h5>
                <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-body">
                <h6>Index (Queue)</h6>
                <ul>
                    <li>Use Filters to narrow the queue by status, date range, or identifiers.</li>
                    <li>Pending inspections are generated automatically for quarantined lots.</li>
                    <li>Open Details to review the lot, reason, and evidence.</li>
                </ul>

                <h6>Details (Decision)</h6>
                <ul>
                    <li>Review product, lot, location, and expiration date.</li>
                    <li>Add decision notes and optional evidence file.</li>
                    <li><strong>Approve</strong> releases the lot and unblocks inventory balances.</li>
                    <li><strong>Reject</strong> keeps the lot quarantined.</li>
                </ul>

                <h6>Evidence</h6>
                <ul>
                    <li>Evidence files can be uploaded during the decision process.</li>
                    <li>Download evidence to audit past decisions.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
